readable.content: A couple in wedding outfits watch the sea from behind a wooden railing . A man and a woman in wedding clothes look out toward the water . A woman in a long white bridal gown and a man in a black suit are standing at a rail looking at the ocean . A woman in a white wedding gown with gold trim standing with a man in a black suit . The groom stands at a railing by the sea with his arm around the bride .
